Further information
The Serbian Ministry of Health website gives up to date information on the number of cases confirmed and tests carried out in Serbia. It includes regional data maps. This website also includes helpline telephone numbers.
If you need urgent consular assistance, contact your nearest British embassy, high commission or consulate. All telephone numbers are available 24/7.
